headline: Has Applied Materials Stock Run Too Far After Its 63.5% 2025 Surge?
summary: Wondering if Applied Materials is still a smart buy after a huge multi year run, or if you are turning up late to the party? This breakdown will help you decide whether the current price makes sense. The stock just closed around $268 after climbing 6.2% over the last week, 16.5% in a month, and 63.5% year to date, building on multi year gains of 156.5% over 3 years and 216.9% over 5 years. Those kinds of returns have come as investors focus on Applied Materials role in enabling advanced chip...
